defaultThe IPCC is a highly effective 
defaultmechanism for asse
defaultssing scientific knowledge
default. It is 
defaultindependent, transparent and 
defaultattracts top scientists who give of their own time to participate. It has well laid out procedures and is open to both expert and Government Review. We see no evidence that it has deliberately sought to justify political commitment or indeed to propose a p
defaultolicy response. 
